examples.en: He told us a story involving life on a farm.
There have been four accidents involving Forest Service planes.
There was a major scandal involving the mayor's ties with the Mob.
The scenes involving the snotty, callous dean ring false right from the start.
...a celebrated imbroglio involving some big names in the New York literary scene...
A verbal disagreement at the football game soon turned into a general melee involving scores of spectators.
